lown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賺到嘅錢損港不利己"},{"pid":"637cf924c262666dfa23b080cdf7dfe6f13b57d6","tid":1963743,"uid":106929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9906d398043910ad946799c07a7228bba93443c7","tid":1963743,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:42:02.000Z","msg":"政府個個樓王<br />\n樓市加辣等於玩鳩自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:49:39.000Z","msg":"屯地 攪當房 炒樓 咩都齊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"940bccbf59e6c37cdd3a46e00367dc3cc715b011","tid":1963743,"uid":54326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:52:16.000Z","msg":"廢張心諗唔保住經濟 我啲樓點走阿 等我走晒先幫你地推冧佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3b6110c8d4bec7a42b71b11a182150f407a817","tid":1963743,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab2efd26e31f687bac9eb3b1a93c116431a9f5ed","tid":1963743,"uid":83251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:39:27.000Z","msg":"又炒樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T11:49:40.000Z","msg":"高薪養貪<br />\n高官根本唔應該炒樓<br />\n不過係人都知成個中共港共官員應該係華人最有錢果班"}]}